      "beat_id": "B01",
      "t_start": 16.0,
      "estimated_duration_s": 17.0,
      "narration_text": "The Brutalist system has seven stages. Ideas to Script to Audio to Visuals to Assemble to Variants to Publish. The entry point for all of them is one command: dot-slash-art. That badge is the whole pipeline.",
